  "fatigueRedFlagOrthostaticAdvisory": "Your fatigue worsens when standing or sitting upright. It may indicate your body has difficulty maintaining stable blood pressure or pulse when upright. It is common in people with EDS. It is worth mentioning to your doctor.",
